snippet.title: Chrono Trigger: Flames Of Eternity Short Gameplay (SNES)
snippet.description:
Today in Gameplay Showcase I show fan game sequel of Chrono Trigger called "Flames Of Eternity". This fan game is only worthy ancestor of Chrono Trigger (Chrono Cross for me isn't). I show you the intro of this fan game, first boss and first and interesting dungeon (I hate the "Trolling Golem")-v Dalton's Dungeon. 

And of course this is my first (blind) playthrought of this game and after this few minutes I am really amused of worg of creators of this fan game, butone thing is making me confused. Why Magus told the elder his true name (Janus)?
